npm i -g create-react-app 


----------When you want to generate app---------------
> go inside the folder where you want to generate app
> create-react-app firstapp

---------Run the application--------
> go inside the app folder
> npm start
> http://localhost:3000

React     > React is the main lib
React-DOM > Help to render the content
React-Script > Help to run the application

function add(a,b){
    var out = [a,b]
    return out
}

add(1,2)
