/////////////////////////////
Type Of Component
//////////////////////
Class Component
> Logical Component
> Any logic or api call will happen in class component
> state managmenent can happen here
> heavy as compare to function 

Functional
> Dumb Component
> We use them for display purpose
> State cannot be manage here

State 
> Act like a local variable
> Every class component can have its own State
> State value can be updated
> Any data interaction happen in app will be through State

Props
> Way to Transfer the data
> VaLUE OF PROPS CANNOT updated
> Props can be use in both funtional and class component

props can pass data from parent to child & Child to parent
but it should be nested


